WEBVTT

00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:05.550
Choose a probability, tau, and invert the
fitted conditional distribution.

00:00:06.150 --> 00:00:10.250
The result is the GDP value where that
distribution reaches tau.

00:00:10.750 --> 00:00:17.750
Here, one npqreg() call directly traces
the 25th, 50th, and 75th conditional

00:00:17.750 --> 00:00:19.750
quantiles across Italy's ordered years.

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:23.650
The curves show the lower, middle,
and upper parts of the distribution.

00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:26.480
The full script is on Gallery Video Demos.
